{"tid":1777503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你知道嗎? 當個個都覺得慢慢靜左落黎嘅時候，黑警已經開始緊大規模秋後算帳","createTime":"2019-12-10T09:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T08:58:28.000Z","uid":66260,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"aed22911892e49564421ab8ffbffa69b91af0d10","tid":1777503,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1777407/page/1?post=10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1777407/page/1?post=10</a><br />\n9月7日沙田站衝突 女被告月餅罐襲警被<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">加控暴動罪</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1777299/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1777299/page/1</a><br />\n飛機維修員涉以環保袋打凹警車車門 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">事隔四個月被控</span></strong>今提堂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1767280/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1767280/page/1</a><br />\n兩男涉 8.11 黃埔藏攻擊性武器 被<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">加控</span></strong>非法集結等罪 將轉介區院審理<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1763277/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1763277/page/1</a><br />\n周四集會涉藏鐳射筆男子身上<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">發現冰毒 被加控</span></strong>一罪<br />\n<br />\n和理非又好勇武又好, 請記住所有野仲未完<br />\n千祈千祈唔好停落黎"},{"pid":"1f03d81aee4c1c95d6ace35f1d6f5e21572836f7","tid":1777503,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9a24171e7fc8c6915f7f12cc4b65f44bcacb34","tid":1777503,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:21:57.000Z","msg":"以上新聞只係冰山一角<br />\n一停落黎, 6000個被捕手足下場係點將會難以想像"},{"pi